Package houses

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GoogleMapsPage
    This class puts an embedded browser in the scene, which can render HTML content from local and remote URLs.
    HouseOverview
    This class creates the main house viewing slide within the EyeView software.
    HouseReviews
    This class creates the reviews page for a specific house advert.
    ImageGallery
    This class groups together the image gallery with rectangles to cover thumbnails that are out of bounds, and set the background of the thumbnails.
    ImageGallery.GalleryPictures
    This class defines the functionality of the image gallery.
    ImageGallery.Thumbnail
    This class creates a small image of specific size, given by the thumbnailHeight and thumbnailHeight constants.
    MoreInfo
    This class creates the information page for a specific house advert.
    VideoPage
    This class creates the video tour page within the EyeView software.
